OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775574665
OL,3,CRegime change attempts in Iran a
OL,4,Cfailure, Houthis tell ITV News
OL,6,FA senior figure in Yemen's Houthi
OL,7,Frebel movement has told ITV News that
OL,8,FIran's regime will not fall because
OL,9,Fthe United States has pursued an
OL,10,F"Israel First" approach that sidelines
OL,11,Fits own interests and strengthens
OL,12,FTehran.
OL,14,FIn written responses to questions from
OL,15,FITV News, Mohammed Ali Al Houthi
OL,16,Fborrowed the language of US President
OL,17,FDonald Trump to dismiss suggestions
OL,18,Fthat the conflict could bring down
OL,19,FIran's leadership, saying it has
OL,20,Fconsolidated support for the regime
OL,21,Finstead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775574665
OL,3,CRegime change attempts in Iran a
OL,4,Cfailure, Houthis tell ITV News
OL,6,F"The result of the aggression is that
OL,7,Fthe Iranian people have rallied around
OL,8,Ftheir regime more than ever before, as
OL,9,Fpolls confirm," he said.
OL,11,F"As for the continuation of the
OL,12,FIranian leadership, the outcome is
OL,13,Fpositive for its people and the
OL,14,Fnation, as it is based on genuine
OL,15,Fpopular support," he added.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775574665
OL,3,CRegime change attempts in Iran a
OL,4,Cfailure, Houthis tell ITV News
OL,6,F"The Muslim Iranian people are
OL,7,Fsteadfast and strong, and they have
OL,8,Fthe right to a national leadership
OL,9,Fthat does not submit to enemies or
OL,10,Faccept their hegemony."
OL,12,FDespite rhetoric from Tehran, he
OL,13,Fstopped short of threatening to shut
OL,14,Fthe Bab al-Mandeb Strait - one of the
OL,15,Fworld's most critical shipping lanes,
OL,16,Foff Yemen's western coast.
OL,18,F"Yemen is acting in accordance with
OL,19,Fits responsibilities to maintain the
OL,20,Fsecurity of the Red Sea," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775574665
OL,3,CRegime change attempts in Iran a
OL,4,Cfailure, Houthis tell ITV News
OL,6,F"What threatens the security of
OL,7,Fnavigation and the Red Sea are the
OL,8,Faggressive military actions of America
OL,9,Fand Israel."
OL,11,FThat position contradicts signals from
OL,12,FIran.
OL,14,FShortly after Al Houthi's responses
OL,15,Fwere sent to ITV News, Ali Akbar
OL,16,FVelayati - a former Iranian foreign
OL,17,Fminister and influential figure in
OL,18,FTehran - warned in a post on X that
OL,19,F"the unified command of the resistance
OL,20,Ffront views Bab al-Mandeb as it does
OL,21,FHormuz".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
