OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775574665
OL,3,CRegime change attempts in Iran a
OL,4,Cfailure, Houthis tell ITV News
OL,6,FIn November 2023, the Houthis began
OL,7,Fattacking commercial ships in the Red
OL,8,FSea, severely impacting access to the
OL,9,FSuez Canal, in what they claimed was
OL,10,Fsupport for Palestinians in Gaza.
OL,12,FBut the Houthis have responded to the
OL,13,Fmost recent US-Israeli conflict
OL,14,Fagainst Iran with caution.
OL,16,FOn March 28, they launched their first
OL,17,Fmissile attack on Israel in support of
OL,18,FIran, saying operations would continue
OL,19,Funtil their objectives are met.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775574665
OL,3,CRegime change attempts in Iran a
OL,4,Cfailure, Houthis tell ITV News
OL,6,FBut the strikes have been limited,
OL,7,Fintercepted by Israeli defences - and
OL,8,Fthe group has not yet returned to
OL,9,Ftargeting commercial shipping.
OL,11,FSeveral weeks into the conflict, that
OL,12,Frestraint is telling. Distracted at
OL,13,Fhome, the Houthis' reluctance to
OL,14,Fescalate - despite their alignment
OL,15,Fwith Tehran - adds weight to the
OL,16,Fargument that the so-called "axis of
OL,17,Fresistance" is not acting with the
OL,18,Fcohesion or force it once projected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
