PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775574665
OL,3,CRegime change attempts in Iran a
OL,4,Cfailure, Houthis tell ITV News
OL,6,F"We take our positions independently,"
OL,7,Fhe said of the Houthis and the Iranian
OL,8,Fregime.
OL,10,F"Yemen is independent in its decisions
OL,11,Fand positions, and it shares with Iran
OL,12,Fand the rest of the axis a
OL,13,Fliberationist orientation and a
OL,14,Ffraternal relationship."
OL,16,FHe said Houthi support would extend to
OL,17,Fother Arab countries if they were to
OL,18,Fbe attacked by Israel - "even if it is
OL,19,FSaudi Arabia, which is attacking us".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775574665
OL,3,CRegime change attempts in Iran a
OL,4,Cfailure, Houthis tell ITV News
OL,6,FBut asked about the humanitarian
OL,7,Fconsequences of the conflict, he
OL,8,Frejected criticism of the group's
OL,9,Fchoices.
OL,11,F"The consequences are a result of the
OL,12,Faggressive actions of the US and
OL,13,FIsrael. You must call things by their
OL,14,Fproper names," he said, claiming that
OL,15,FWashington had, "adopted the Israel
OL,16,FFirst principle instead of America
OL,17,FFirst".
OL,26,@vD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
